## Overview
This directory contains a structured budgeting model used to manage personal income, expenditure, savings, and financial commitments.

The objective is to ensure personal finances are:

- visible  
- controlled  
- sustainable  
- aligned to goals  

Strong budgeting enables informed decisions and long-term financial resilience.

