## Control Principles Embedded in This Toolkit

### 1) Visibility Drives Control
You cannot manage what you cannot see.

### 2) Prioritise Commitments
Essential obligations come first.

### 3) Plan Savings Intentionally
Savings should be structured, not accidental.

### 4) Review Regularly
Consistency improves accuracy and behaviour.

### 5) Early Adjustment
Small corrections prevent larger problems.

